(17, '', 'ศาสตราจารย์', 'Professor Emeritus', 'ดร.', '', 'นงนุช', 'Nongnuch', 'Vanittanakom', 'วณิตย์ธนาคม', '', 'For her academic career, from 1980 to 1986, she worked at Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Siriraj Hospital, Mahidol University, Bangkok. Since 1987, she moved to work at the Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University. Presently, N. Vanittanakom is a Professor in Microbiology. In February 2016, she received Professor Emeritus Honor from Her Royal Highness Princess Sirindhorn. She is mainly interested in Medical Mycology. She was participated as an invited speaker in several international conferences, for examples, the Congress of the International Society for Human and Animal Mycology (ISHAM), the Asean Conference in Medical Laboratory Technology, the International Conference on Opportunistic Pathogens in AIDS, the International Mycology Congress (IMC) and the International Congress of Mycology (IUMS).', '', 'drnongnuch@gmail.com', '', '0', '', 'uploads/staff/noungnuch.jpg', 'Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University \r\nTel: 053-935332', '<b>1985  Dr.rer.nat. (cum laude) degree<b>, the Eberhard-Karls- University of Tübingen, Germany</br>\r\n<b>1992   Alexander von Humboldt Postdoctoral Research Fellow<b> at the Microbial Genetics, Faculty of Biology, Eberhard-Karls- University of Tübingen</br>\r\n<b>1994  Research Fellow</b> of the Fogarty National Institute of Health, Johns Hopkins University, USA\r\n', '2016-10-31 13:30:16', '2016-10-15 16:13:28'),
(18, '', 'ผู้ช่วยศาสตราจารย์', 'Assistant Professor', 'ดร.', '', 'กุลวดี', 'Kulwadee', 'Phannachet', 'พรรณเชษฐ์', '', '1. Epidemiology of antibiotic resistance genes in bacterial clinical isolates                                                               \r\n2. Molecular characterization of antibiotic resistance plasmids', '', 'kulwadee.p@cmu.ac.th', '', '0', '', 'uploads/staff/kunwadee.jpg', 'Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University \r\nTel: 053-935332', '<b>1992  B.Sc. (Medical technology)</b>, Chiang Mai University, Chiang Mai, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>1998  M.Sc. (Molecular Genetics-Genetic enginerring)</b>, Mahidol University, Bangkok, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>2005  Ph.D. (Biochemistry)</b>, University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign, Illinois, USA\r\n', '2016-10-31 13:30:42', '2016-10-15 16:14:52'),
(19, '', 'ผู้ช่วยคณบดีผ่ายวิชาการ', 'Assistance Dean of Academic Affair', 'ดร.พญ.', '', 'วรลักษณ์', 'Volaluck', 'Supajatura', 'สัปจาตุระ', '', '1. Allergy and Immunology                                                  \r\n2. Wound healing', '', 'volaluck.supajatura@gmail.com', '', '0', '', 'uploads/staff/voraluck.jpg', 'Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University \r\nTel: 053-935147', '<b>1982 B.Sc. (Medical Technology)</b>, Chiang Mai University, Chiang Mai, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>1985 M.Sc. (Microbiology)</b>, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University, Chiang Mai, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>1994 M.D.</b>, Chulalongkorn University, Bangkok, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>1996 Diploma in Dermatology</b>, Institute of Dermatology, Department of Medical Service, Ministry of Public Health, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>2002 Ph.D. (Dermatology)</b>, Juntendo University School of Medicine, Japan</br>\r\n<b>2005 หนังสืออนุมัติเวชศาสตร์ครอบครัว</b> ราชวิทยาลัยแพทย์เวชศาสตร์ครอบครัวแห่งประเทศไทย\r\n', '2016-10-31 13:31:03', '2016-10-15 16:17:58'),
(20, '', 'อาจารย์', 'Instructor', 'ดร.', '', 'มาณู', 'Manu', 'Deeudom', 'ดีอุดม', '', 'Our major focus is understanding how environmental factors affect bacterial respiratory metabolism and susceptibility to antibiotics and how bacteria regulate and employ various mechanisms involved in physiological adaptation under changing environment. We also work on nantimicrobial resistance mechanisms, mobile genetic elements, and horizontal gene transfer of multidrug resistance in many bacterial pathogens.', '', 'manu.deeudom@cmu.ac.th', '', '0', '', 'uploads/staff/manu.jpg', 'Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University \r\nTel: 053-935332\r\n', '<b>1995 B.Sc. (Microbiology)</b>, Chiang Mai University, Chiang Mai, Thailand</br>\r\n<b>2001 M.Sc. (Microbiology)</b>, Colorado state University, Colorado, USA</br>\r\n<b>2008 Ph.D. (Biology)</b>, University of York, UK', '2016-10-31 13:31:26', '2016-10-15 16:18:58'),
(21, '', 'ผู้ช่วยศาสตราจารย์', 'Assistant Professor', 'ดร.', '', 'พูนสุข', 'Poonsook', 'Keelapang', 'กีฬาแปง', '', 'Molecular biology and vaccine development of dengue viruses and other flaviviruses', '', 'poonsook.k@cmu.ac.th', '', '0', '', 'uploads/staff/punesook.jpg', 'Department of Microbiology, Faculty of Medicine, Chiang Mai University \r\nTel: 053-935332 ext 421', '<b>1994 Ph.D.</b>, Birkbeck College, University of London, UK', '2016-10-31 13:31:48', '2016-10-15 16:19:27');
